 Adding fields to the Standard Table we do the most common changes
We use this in the Situation How to customize a document layout with out an over layer recipe.
To do this requirement we need a new solution
so create a new project within our Package 


Locate the Standard Table  in the AOT 
Right click on it and choose Create extension 
Make sure all the names must be globally Unique.
open the new table extension in the designer tab.
Locate the Name Edt in AOT and drag it to the Extensio Table on to fields node in the designer 
Rename the Field to Name as required
set the label Property
save it and close designer.
